  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600932480463-YRPPVJKNAN679XUHVV77/6a-nsdggmorphprojecthop.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>Hope you'll consider joining in on the fun at <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/whats-hot/%3Fpp%3D300\">Two Peas In A Bucket</a> this weekend. There are lots of projects and activities going on there as well as <a href=\"http://twopeasinabucket.typepad.com/\">the blog</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600932495025-D4KJLS6XE28T6LZ1M8P4/6b-cha_1a-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>You can see my completed CHA daybook <a href=\"http://www.twopeasinabucket.com/gallery/member/305620-amytangerine/1823347-nsd-make-take-cha-daybook/\">here</a>.</p><p>I am the last stop on the Garden Girl Morph and there are prizes at each stop. Enter by leaving a comment on each layout. <a href=\"http://www.twopeasinabucket.com/gallery/member/6751-shannon-tidwell/1823042-nsd-garden-girl-morph-learning-to-fish/\">Shannon</a>, <a href=\"http://www.twopeasinabucket.com/gallery/member/106721-wilna/1821514-nsd-garden-girl-morph-whazup/\">Wilna</a>, <a href=\"http://www.twopeasinabucket.com/gallery/member/34449-lynnghahary/1822510-nsd-garden-girl-morph-crazy-silly-fun/\">Lynn</a>, <a href=\"http://www.twopeasinabucket.com/gallery/member/6512-wendy-sue/1822810-nsd-garden-girl-morph-19-reason-to-smile/\">Wendy Sue</a>, and <a href=\"http://www.twopeasinabucket.com/gallery/member/305620-amytangerine/1823056-nsd-garden-girl-morph-we-may-be-crazy/\">I</a> had a lot of fun with this project. Happy crafty weekend!</p><p>NOTE: Creativation (formerly CHA) </p>"
